<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然每年都會慶祝，<delay20 />
但老實說我不太清楚<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所謂的農曆新年到底是什麼。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay20 />1月1日加上今天，
就能慶祝兩次新年，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得挺划算的啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很高興可以跟島上的人一起<delay20 />
迎接農曆新年。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為對我來說，<delay8 />
大家就像我的家人一樣啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />農曆新年的時候，<delay8 />
你喜歡怎麼過？<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在家裡悠閒度日？<delay frames="30" />
或者是<delay8 />去參加戶外活動？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管是哪種都得注意別鬧過頭，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />反而讓自己受傷了啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很多人都是跟家人一起<delay8 />慶祝農曆新年的呢……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一聊到這種話題，<delay20 />
就連我也會忍不住<delay8 />懷念老家啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />趁著過年的機會，<delay20 />
寫張心意卡寄給老家的親人吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然這是一年一度的農曆新年，<delay20 />
但說實在的，今天跟往常相比<delay8 />
也沒什麼太大的改變，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是吃得比平常多一點，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />稍微嗨了點，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話比平常多了點嘛！</message>
</msbt>